{"tid":1966840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實泛民同本土都已經過咗時","createTime":"2020-04-10T12:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T17:27:29.000Z","uid":221035,"like":65,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c67a6fb090e6d317fb5593babf0101ee61e1c4","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"唔好誤會，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔係</strong></span></span>要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>批評或者否定</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而係仍然流於<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>泛民、本土、自決、獨派</strong></span></span>呢啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>標籤</strong></span></span>同分類已經<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過時</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔計陳雲嘅城邦論（佢太極端）<br />\n雨傘後展開咗<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本土思潮</span></span></strong>，主張香港係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民族、政治共同體</span></span></strong>，而衍生有人認爲要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自決或者獨立</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月之後嘅抗爭，基本上已經唔可以用本土、泛民呢啲標籤去睇，大家會明點解我話「過時」<br />\n<br />\n宜家真正嘅分歧係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">攬炒/革命/激進派 vs 保守/溫和/改良派</span></strong></span><br />\n前者認爲香港已死、制度已死，要全盤推到重來，香港唔係淨係要民主咁簡單，而係社會制度、教育、人口政策、產業架構等等都要有翻天覆地嘅改變，要有新香港<br />\n五大訴求只係其中一環，大家過咗大半年都會明就算攞曬五大訴求，如果政策唔變、制度唔變，香港根本就無好到，都一樣係好多人suffer<br />\n<br />\n後者認爲有險可守，香港有空間慢慢改進，拒絕攬炒<br />\n<br />\n呢到唔係要批評或者話後者錯，完全唔係咁嘅意思<br />\n只不過，我希望對新香港有想象嘅朋友可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">團結</span></span></strong>起來，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>用本土、自決、獨派呢啲去<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">互相標籤</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我哋應該互相支持，一齊建設新香港嘅藍圖，憑住攬炒嘅意志，去對現有嘅制度徹底砍掉重練、奪權，盼望可以掀起新嘅思潮，團結抗爭力量組織新嘅政治力量&mdash;&mdash;真正嘅攬炒/革命/激進派</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你認同呢個想法，不妨留低正評同share呢個post出去，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">讓大家知道我哋唔係少數，我哋唔係孤獨嘅！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"69fa62342056e72eb5fd7d71a39d018eda493b9d","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"如果覺得你兩者都唔係，不妨花啲時間思考吓你嘅政治理念"},{"pid":"f3037c95c6220d8cb1bee8f32d65b2317d98efa9","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"再分咩本土、獨派其實已經冇乜意思，我哋要團結"},{"pid":"ae8a7f699386c7721430e472660c57755000ebc7","tid":1966840,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"真&middot;攬炒派&mdash;&mdash;白票兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b052eb0a384a53f2b1682d58d7812cc04359c96","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae8a7f699386c7721430e472660c57755000ebc7","tid":1966840,"uid":177213,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"真&middot;攬炒派&mdash;&mdash;白票兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"佢哋算數啦，唔好提佢哋"},{"pid":"c9f1571b13e3d5171c8f7593f6481b0428c691b1","tid":1966840,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"327e65a3e2569c942e0ecb5968b3647770922533","tid":1966840,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d752491efa026943724f04