66840,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c67a6fb090e6d317fb5593babf0101ee61e1c4","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"唔好誤會，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔係</strong></span></span>要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>批評或者否定</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而係仍然流於<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>泛民、本土、自決、獨派</strong></span></span>呢啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>標籤</strong></span></span>同分類已經<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過時</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔計陳雲嘅城邦論（佢太極端）<br />\n雨傘後展開咗<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本土思潮</span></span></strong>，主張香港係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民族、政治共同體</span></span></strong>，而衍生有人認爲要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自決或者獨立</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月之後嘅抗爭，基本上已經唔可以用本土、泛民呢啲標籤去睇，大家會明點解我話「過時」<br />\n<br />\n宜家真正嘅分歧係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">攬炒/革命/激進派 vs 保守/溫和/改良派</span></strong></span><br />\n前者認爲香港已死、制度已死，要全盤推到重來，香港唔係淨係要民主咁簡單，而係社會制度、教育、人口政策、產業架構等等都要有翻天覆地嘅改變，要有新香港<br />\n五大訴求只係其中一環，大家過咗大半年都會明就算攞曬五大訴求，如果政策唔變、制度唔變，香港根本就無好到，都一樣係好多人suffer<br />\n<br />\n後者認爲有險可守，香港有空間慢慢改進，拒絕攬炒<br />\n<br />\n呢到唔係要批評或者話後者錯，完全唔係咁嘅意思<br />\n只不過，我希望對新香港有想象嘅朋友可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">團結</span></span></strong>起來，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>用本土、自決、獨派呢啲去<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">互相標籤</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我哋應該互相支持，一齊建設新香港嘅藍圖，憑住攬炒嘅意志，去對現有嘅制度徹底砍掉重練、奪權，盼望可以掀起新嘅思潮，團結抗爭力量組織新嘅政治力量&mdash;&mdash;真正嘅攬炒/革命/激進派</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你認同呢個想法，不妨留低正評同share呢個post出去，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">讓大家知道我哋唔係少數，我哋唔係孤獨嘅！</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a925454a9b5ea9280771775263058ea667a2a9","tid":1966840,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"幫推文"},{"pid":"0dedd792781b4701a2e7cbb3346637a22136335d","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a982e2788a4e474654a4fb2952ab676e60000596","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8aac83dad269240c1285b31be771507393706f","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8aa53970a88af2b8982d0cc686b02edb499b723","tid":1966840,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"但你呢個都唔係political ideology"},{"pid":"9eff1ca5d9424ec63196865d18709afd9cd34596","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace633208020f5478304a5963b866e591f28860e","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8aa53970a88af2b8982d0cc686b02edb499b723","tid":1966840,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"但你呢個都唔係political ideology"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"唔完全係ideology嘅劃分嚟，其實一路以來<br />\n更大程度係路線之爭<br />\n只不過宜家唔應該用舊嘅cleavage"},{"pid":"0d41337e193764a119f129134a68011e0514ffb5","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b091e70c21214be4143a4fe714a306de26bd61","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ee71a614383aaaf73126bea699b25f98dca14c","tid":1966840,"uid":61914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9892d6e66f9e2221c1b7c785c03be9fc3d60692c","tid":1966840,"uid":173814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"係班熱狗要扮本土黎打擊泛民姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"到要求佢地做返本土派要做既嘢個陣，呢班人就會走夾唔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實正常人都睇通哂，用黎用去都係呢類招數 包括陳雲白兵之流"},{"pid":"7315333400f16ec845dfac807a161df059b42af9","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8ff75ad1d2e7e1fad6b61f3af51856666904e5","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d87dbcb81bd9b3002351b45f4ee24e9cf156d25","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9022299af13cfe9329e8b611d4665082f948bc90","tid":1966840,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":